                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>he battalion draws and hurls alchemical bombs with practiced precision. The bombs rain down in a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 30 feet that deals @Damage[3d8[fire],1d4[persistent,fire]|options:area-damage]{3d8 fire damage and 1d4 persistent fire damage} damage (@Check[reflex|dc:22|basic] save). When the troop is reduced to 2 segments, this area decreases to a @Template[type:burst|distance:5]. Creatures adjacent to the burst take 1d4 splash fire damage.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
