                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> to <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span></p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The battalion stabs with their pikes at enemies in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] (@Check[reflex|dc:22|basic] save). The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[(1d6+1)[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(2d6+8)[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(3d6+10)[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>"
